            . I am a pawnbroker. I have three pieces of paper, pawned by the prisoner on the 16th of September, in the name of John Sorlter.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18291029-224-person1851">
                  DANIEL 
                  DUTCH
               <interp inst="t18291029-224-person1851" type="surname" value="DUTCH"></interp>
