                     <interp inst="t18291029-224-person1851" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, and found three rooms had been papered with this paper, at No. 1, Grosvenor-place, Chelsea, where the witness took them, and these three pieces were pawned at Chelsea.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. He saw the wife of the person it was for<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182910290088"></xptr>come up stairs with a child in her arms; here is the bill of parcels the prosecutor gave me - I was obliged to make away with the rest of it, as Mr. Kenyon was not at home.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18291029-224-person1852">
                  JEFFERY 
                  JOLLY
               <interp inst="t18291029-224-person1852" type="surname" value="JOLLY"></interp>
