                     <interp inst="t18291029-224-person1852" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . This bill was made out for the gentleman he stated it was for - I went to the house, and the woman refused to tell me any thing about the prisoner - I understand he has been paid for it.</p>
